 frequently than other owners &ndash; around 0.3 times per year &ndash; with a lower probability of severe problems than with other compact cars.<br />\n<br />\nConsumer Reports gives the 2010-2018 Mazda3 model years an impressive reliability rating of either four or five (out of five), while the newest 2019 and 2020 models receive a more surprising rating of three. Nearly every model year receives Consumer Reports&rsquo; seal of recommendation.<br />\n<br />\n幾好，有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f768a7fbd6897fea8d7982ea4980e8c896f1b6","tid":2492923,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T17:21:12.000Z","msg":"有人話甩轆都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef46a3e662c26ceb4a6239e6ea8b3ec999e25c84","tid":2492923,"uid":260744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02f768a7fbd6897fea8d7982ea4980e8c896f1b6","tid":2492923,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T17:21:12.000Z","msg":"有人話甩轆都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T17:23:19.000Z","msg":"gen 3 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， gen 4爆炸都唔關我事啦"},{"pid":"20c53f9a929545ca6b9cbc143dcd24efb3c13111","tid":2492923,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/buy/2020-Mazda-Mazda3/recalls/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.autoblog.com%2Fbuy%2F2020-Mazda-Mazda3%2Frecalls%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL0B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=df23799f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.autoblog.com/buy/2020-Mazda-Mazda3/recalls/</a><br />\n<br />\nqc一流"},{"pid":"9c5cf49b014cc3d2114d20eaae1ac47f89fb28d2","tid":2492923,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infu